    <item>
      <title>德国和法国推动更积极的关税回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国和德国正在推动对美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的关税措施做出更强有力的反应，并提倡有力的报复，这可以加强欧盟的谈判立场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/germany-and-france-push-for-a-more-aggressive-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 10:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国咖啡饮用者面对价格较高的杯子，关税命中了主要供应商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-coffee-drinkers-face-pricier-cup-as-tariffs-hit-key-supplier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的广泛关税措施袭击了越南最大的供应商之一越南，咖啡在美国有可能变得更加昂贵。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-coffee-drinkers-face-pricier-cup-as-tariffs-hit-key-supplier</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:26:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贸易商付出更多痛苦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的大量贸易关税将击败美国经济，因此彭博社的货币量最高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/dollar-slides-on-concern-trump-s-tariffs-will-batter-us-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:01:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自特朗普赢得以来，美国的10年收益率首次下降到4％以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自10月以来，基准国库的收益率首次跌至4％以下，因为华尔街对美国经济将从唐纳德·特朗普总统的贸易战争中最终变得更糟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/us-10-year-yield-drops-toward-4-as-tariffs-fuel-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:09:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着债券的集会，股票途径加深关税冲击：市场包装</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球市场中，“美国第一”贸易正在瓦解，股票与美元旁边急剧暴露在美国经济上。随着华尔街对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税战争的叛乱加剧，商人急忙进入固定收入的避风港。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 23:34:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>不列颠哥伦比亚省在四年内获得第四个学分降级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省的信用评级已被S＆amp; p全球评级和穆迪投资者服务所削减，因为较低的移民和贸易不确定性会使加拿大省的经济增长与政府支出不断增加的同时。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/british-columbia-gets-fourth-credit-downgrade-in-four-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 21:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
